question: Which illness is most common in warmer climates?
answers:
SELECT c.description, COUNT(c.description) 
FROM conditions c 
JOIN patients p ON c.patient = p.id 
JOIN encounters e ON c.encounter = e.id 
JOIN organizations o ON e.organization = o.id 
WHERE o.lat > 30 AND o.lat < 40 
GROUP BY c.description 
ORDER BY COUNT(c.description) DESC 
LIMIT 1;

question: Which illness is most common in warmer climates?
answers:
SELECT c.description, COUNT(c.description) 
FROM conditions c 
JOIN patients p ON c.patient = p.id 
JOIN encounters e ON c.encounter = e.id 
JOIN organizations o ON e.organization = o.id 
WHERE o.lat > 30 AND o.lat < 40 
GROUP BY c.description 
ORDER BY COUNT(c.description) DESC 
LIMIT 1;
